About Me

I am a skilled and enthusiastic technology professional with extensive experience in using information technology and data to make the right business decisions and improve business processes. I am a data analyst and a business analyst, but I also have a background in biological sciences, statistics and software development. I use python, SQL and Tableau for my data work.

I have worked in different industries throughout my career, ranging from medical science, marketing, research and government. I currently work in business analytics and data management in the tertiary education sector.

Outside of work, I am into photography, fibre arts , Broadway musicals, travel and chess.

I am currently based in Wollongong, NSW, Australia.
